OL,5, Inconsistent monitoring of asbestos in 
OL,6, Welsh schools could put pupils and     
OL,7, staff at risk, unions have warned.     
OL,9,FA Freedom of Information (FoI) request 
OL,10,Fby BBC Wales shows more than 900       
OL,11,Fschools are known to contain asbestos. 
OL,13,FMost are regularly inspected, but some 
OL,14,Fsurveys are 10 years old and often     
OL,15,Fasbestos is suspected but not known.   
OL,16,FUnions want urgent action to be taken. 
OL,18,FThe Welsh Local Government Association 
OL,19,Fsaid councils worked to "eliminate any 
OL,20,Frisks as quickly as possible".         
